long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Explore the mysterious world of Sprunki Parasite, an extraordinary mod of the popular music game Incredibox. 

Wondering What Is Sprunki Parasite? 
It’s a dark twist on music creation that lets you compose haunting, eerie tunes using an array of unique, unsettling characters. 

How to play? 
Simply visit our official website at https://sprunkiparasite.online/ and dive into a chilling soundscape designed to captivate and inspire. 

Discover Game Features that blend music, mystery, and a hint of the macabre, perfect for fans of dark aesthetics and innovative gameplay. Let Sprunki Parasite guide your creativity into the shadows—compose eerie soundscapes and experience music like never before.
